# SOKRATES Project Rules

## Training Commands
- DO NOT automatically run training commands (SFT, DPO, trace generation)
- Only provide commands for the user to run manually
- User will execute training when ready

## Documentation
- Keep docs/ files numerically ordered (00_, 01_, 02_, etc.)
- Update 00_index.md when adding new docs

## Hardware
- Available GPUs: 0-7 (B200, 183GB each)
- GPU 0 is often occupied - prefer GPUs 2-7
- Use CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES to select GPUs

## Key Paths
- SFT model: outputs/sft/latest/final
- Training data: data/processed/prontoqa_train.jsonl
- Test data: data/processed/prontoqa_test.jsonl

